### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

###

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doctor@hospital.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123",
  "name": "Dr. John Doe",
  "role": "Resident"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doctor@hospital.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

###

### Get Profile (replace TOKEN with actual token from login)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get All Patients
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Create Patient
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patients
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "age": 65,
  "gender": "M",
  "diagnosis": "Community-acquired pneumonia",
  "room": "401A",
  "admissionDate": "2025-12-10",
  "acuity": "Watch",
  "isolation": "Droplet",
  "underlyingConditions": "DM Type 2, HTN",
  "allergies": "Penicillin",
  "medications": [],
  "tasks": []
}

###

### Get Patient Statistics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patients/statistics
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Add Task to Patient (replace PATIENT_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patients/PATIENT_ID/tasks
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Check morning labs",
  "priority": "Before Noon"
}

###

### Add Medication to Patient (replace PATIENT_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patients/PATIENT_ID/medications
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ceftriaxone",
  "dose": "2g",
  "route": "IV",
  "frequency": "q24h"
}

###

### Add Lab Result (replace PATIENT_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patients/PATIENT_ID/labs
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "labType": "creatinine",
  "date": "2025-12-13",
  "value": 1.2
}

###
